ActExport and Import Permits Act
SubjectOrder Amending the Export Control List (Arms Trade Treaty)
PrecisOrder Amending the EXPORT CONTROL LIST (ARMS TRADE TREATY) (ATT) in order to amend the Export Control List to (1) set out in detail, in a distinct and identifiable group, the eight ATT categories of Full-system conventional arms; and (2) require permits for the export of all items in the new group to the United States.
